    <Title>Cisco TelePresence TC and TE Software Crafted Packets Denial of Service Vulnerability</Title>
    <ID SystemName="Cisco Bug ID">CSCuj68952</ID>
    <Notes>
      <Note Title="Summary" Type="Summary" Ordinal="3">A vulnerability in the network drivers of Cisco TelePresence TC and TE
Software  could allow an unauthenticated, remote attacker to cause
several processes to restart and possibly reload the affected system.



The
vulnerability is due to insufficient implementation of flood controls.
An attacker could exploit this vulnerability by sending crafted IP
packets at a high rate.</Note>
      <Note Title="Cisco Bug IDs" Type="Other" Ordinal="5">CSCuj68952</Note>
    </Notes>
